description: Removes an ingress authorization rule from a Client VPN endpoint.

parameters.name: ClientVpnEndpointId
parameters.description: The ID of the Client VPN endpoint with which the authorization rule is associated.

parameters.name: TargetNetworkCidr
parameters.description: The IPv4 address range, in CIDR notation, of the network for which access is being removed.

nested_items.name: Code
nested_items.description: The state of the authorization rule.

nested_items.name: Message
nested_items.description: A message about the status of the authorization rule, if applicable.
